name: Paw-awssignature4dynamicvalue
tagline: A Paw Extension to compute authentication signatures for AWS API access.
body: Generates [AWS Signature 4](http://docs.aws.amazon.com/general/latest/gr/signature-version-4.html) headers for Paw by Lucky Marmot. This web site is here to "lock" in a domain to use in the extension.
